 <PERSON> Douglas </PERSON> <PERSON> Grant </PERSON> <PERSON> Mine </PERSON>, based in <LOCATION> San </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Salvador </LOCATION>, covers <LOCATION> Central </LOCATION> <LOCATION> America </LOCATION> for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>.
